author_ssm: Christine George with additions by Catherine Newton
unittitle_ssm: Friends of City Hall Park Papers
abstract_ssm: The Friends of City Hall Park Papers contain materials from the Friends of City Hall Park, an advocacy group, and its campaigns to better City Hall Park in lower Manhattan. Within this collection are materials pertaining to the park itself as well as other organizations that assisted Friends of City Hall Park. The materials include correspondence, ephemera, newspaper clippings, and maps.
